Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:48.21,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないから　あなたのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:52.17,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんなに時間が経っても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:22:01.06,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}うまく言えない　気持ちばかり溢れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:14.75,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日も空は続いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:19.21,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}けれど違う風が流れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:24.04,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何度祈りは捧げられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:29.15,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そのうち幾つ届いたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:37.40,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歴史はいつも遠い物語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:42.46,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向く余裕さえ無く人は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:49.26,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}先を急いでいくけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:55.16,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}守りたいから　あなたのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:59.16,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんなの離ればなれでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:07.69,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが私の願いの全てだと言える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:48.21,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的身影像首歌 縈繞在我心窩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:52.17,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伴著時光從我前方飛過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:22:01.06,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那些無以言表的 心緒還有情思佔據了每一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:14.75,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這一天天空依然晴朗開闊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:19.21,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻悄悄讓奇異微風輕輕的吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:24.04,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無數次向著它們默默祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:29.15,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能傳到的卻不知道有幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:37.40,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歷史總悄無聲息 只留下美麗的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:42.46,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無暇流連這般悠遠的人兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:49.26,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向目標 一步一步不停的奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:55.16,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的身影像首歌 願緊緊守候著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:59.16,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使無盡的時空 離散了你我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:07.69,edchi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這些願望像星光 照亮我心房 全為你熠熠閃爍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋諾斯 統治大陸的女王的王都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的鬥士為了成為新任女王 均以該地為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們將各自的心事寄於刀刃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續著『Queen's Blade』的熱斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟著我到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼嘛 「出門靠旅伴處世靠人情」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然蹦出來 你算什麼旅伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是『聖乳』 神聖之極
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 你就要努力不讓『聖乳』溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？或許有些困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:01:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若『聖乳』全灑光之時 等待你的將是即刻墜入冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此這般 我想早點回天界都回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們不慌不忙地慢慢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是安逸輕鬆的一條直路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是到了一個像樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前真是吃了大苦頭呢 巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們在抵達目的地前不會死在外面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是『Queen's Blade』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抵達目的地也是一種戰鬥 差不多就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 在那之前就有問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 接下來我們要走哪條路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從日之本帶來的地圖太老了 基本靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最主要的問題就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人是個非比尋常的方向癡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捂臉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得太多了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人 這究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就在這裡洗去旅途的疲勞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛兵 太陽要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備野營 去找合適的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我馬上去找更衣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個機靈的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她是自願來參加這次長途旅行 或許有些隱情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 能幹事就好管她有什麼隱情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在這附近有一處溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這水真不錯 巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使遠隔萬里 但這暗紅色與日之本別無兩樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一想我們還真是來到了一個很遙遠的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬嘶聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去看看 巴大人在這裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗娜大人 很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這樣單獨行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去洗洗汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洋武者嗎…不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去她會與巴大人碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不瞭解大陸 也不清楚西洋武者的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法保證你能再一次活著踏上日之本的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為守衛日之本的利劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這就是生為武者巫女的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論遭遇何種苦難 一切都為了聖上的隆恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而為了日之本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有人先來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『近衛隊長』艾麗娜?巴恩斯將要使用這片溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異族之輩速速離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我先來的 你突然叫我離開…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洋武者都是如此這般欠缺禮儀與冷靜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此 你和我的姐姐戰鬥過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻 我看了直播
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 我感受到了不可思議的緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要參加『Queen's Blade』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事情想要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道去女王之都的路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王之都？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 本來這次旅途很趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在不熟悉的土地上我們一直迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的裝扮很奇特呢 就好像是日之本的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍軍中的一員叛變 妨礙了我們的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有2個女人趁亂登上了這片大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看漏了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王有事情要向日之本的人確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她們帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會在這種地方遇到忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一個普通的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你散發出與我相同的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分 你認了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務本是收集巴恩斯伯爵領地內的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這種情況下 敕命優先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是求之不得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這傢伙獻給阿爾多拉 以此接近那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許那2個女人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把另外一個也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是『Queen's Blade』的鬥士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我參賽只是因為肩負皇國的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我不惜付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會在這裡進行無謂的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我戰鬥是無謂的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會投身於無義的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭 請您慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 怪女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜 你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我獲得自由吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我是想要救她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要永遠在這迷宮裡消耗時間嗎？蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣得我都睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 連人家的肚子都被氣餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是甲魔忍軍的殘黨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原?忍軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼叛變且妨礙我們的忍者就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們忍者所追求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一個正式的舞台 以此展示千錘百煉出來的殺人技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是日之本毀滅的話 只要把自己賣給其他國家便好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是『牙之暗殺團』的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要利用甲魔忍軍襲擊日之本？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人為此付出了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問話的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老早就知道大陸的地下組織一直與忍軍有所接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕後黑手是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜 你在哪裡？靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句話不說就失去了蹤影 此前從未有過這樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是巴小姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請 她受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我把你帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是日之本的武者巫女 讓我不得不利用這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思 你對靜做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔掉武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信條就是「不做無謂事」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣 討厭做無謂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會了 你老老實實地聽我的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 若不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是要砍斷你們的手腳 我也要將你們帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要講話的舌頭還在就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有其他武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 巴大人 這傢伙是日之本死掉同伴的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群傢伙利用甲魔忍軍襲擊了日之本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全脫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定會取得『Queen's Blade』的優勝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人 此時不戰更待何時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法目睹巴大人的英姿…是我唯一的遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我最重要的同伴們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肩負著重要的使命 一路上盡量避免無謂的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在這千里之遙的異鄉之地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了我所珍視的同胞們的仇人 我不認為這是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不如說這是蒼天的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以大義為名 我向你提出進行『Queen's Blade』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Queen's Blade』？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意欲參加『Queen's Blade』的鬥士們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此展示你們所擁有的全部鬥技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我們打開試煉之門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士的名字是『武者巫女』巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之對戰的是『牙之暗殺者』伊爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天界諸神 請欣賞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要被河蟹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺者的臉被公之於眾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種事情 就要我無果而終嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在『Queen's Blade』中過關斬將 打倒女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你因為驕傲而估錯了對手的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『武者蹴擊』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Black Rose』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武者巫女奧義必殺·『風月斬』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}T:這招有個更好D名字『爆衣露膚斬』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓關節脫臼 沒想到還真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住 休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認定伊爾瑪放棄戰鬥 這場比賽巴獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 她比與我戰鬥時強了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著別人轉播成功 感覺真是無明業火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也得努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要違抗我嗎 庫洛德特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再這樣自欺欺人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不僅未能帶回蕾娜 竟然還要參加『Queen's Blade』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為伯爵家的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去參加那種可恨的女王遊戲 真是愚蠢之極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也要讓家門蒙羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生到這個世上就已經是巴恩斯家之恥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有了這種自知之明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算愚弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打心裡深愛著父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望您能相信這點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 祈願巴恩斯家族永遠繁榮昌盛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不惜拋棄一切 就能找到自己所追求的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次與你相見時 我會得出何種答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的我還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蕾娜 我必須去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…再來一砲…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是與蕾娜一起漫無目的亂晃的娜娜艾露
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫無目的的旅途總之就是閒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太閒了 搞得我身體狀況都變差了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 我與雌猴們根本玩不到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是一個大得離奇危險得過分 簡直就是一個不可想像的大胸器要耀武揚威了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家和我一起期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 赤心～武器商與鋼鐵姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此展示你們所擁有的全部鬥技吧


